.DT
broadcast_shop_event
Disk World creator help
broadcast_shop_event

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
broadcast_shop_event -  This method sends the event to all the people who have been set to receive shop events.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int broadcast_shop_event(string type,
object player,
mixed args ...)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the event
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the player in the event
%^BOLD%^args%^RESET%^ - the arguements in the event
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 to supress the default messages
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/shop_event.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sends the event to all the people who have been set to
receive shop events.  The shop event function is called
event_shop(object shop, ...).


If this method returns 1 then the default messages are supressed.
.EP

